&lt;p&gt;We are one of the busiest independent adult hospices in the UK and we are looking for caring Bank Health Care Assistants to provide flexible ad-hoc support on our 28 bed Inpatient Unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our nursing team pride themselves on delivering the highest quality, compassionate care and support to our patients, their families and carers. If you have experience of working as a Health Care Assistant, we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion about the role, please contact Sarah Johnston, Head of IPU by emailing sarah.johnston@thameshospice.org.uk or call 01753 848956&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Appointment is subject to an Enhanced Disclosure and Barring Service check, including barred lists.&lt;/p&gt;
